---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Insurance Options | Financial Management"
  description="Explore insurance options available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about life, health, and other insurance products tailored for veterans' needs.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Insurance Options for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of comprehensive insurance coverage for veterans. This page outlines various insurance options available to veterans, helping you protect yourself and your family against unforeseen circumstances.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Life Insurance</h2>
        <p>Life insurance options tailored for veterans:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Term life insurance policies with veteran-specific terms</li>
          <li>Whole life insurance options with cash value accumulation</li>
          <li>Group life insurance schemes for veteran organisations</li>
          <li>Policies that account for service-related health conditions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Health Insurance</h2>
        <p>Supplementary health coverage options:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Private health insurance to complement NHS care</li>
          <li>Specialist coverage for service-related conditions</li>
          <li>Dental and vision insurance plans</li>
          <li>Mental health coverage options</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Disability Insurance</h2>
        <p>Protection against loss of income due to disability:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Short-term and long-term disability insurance</li>
          <li>Occupation-specific disability coverage</li>
          <li>Supplemental disability insurance to enhance AFCS benefits</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Home and Contents Insurance</h2>
        <p>Protecting your property and belongings:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Specialised home insurance for adapted properties</li>
          <li>Contents insurance with coverage for mobility equipment</li>
          <li>Discounted rates for veterans through partner insurers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Travel Insurance</h2>
        <p>Coverage for veterans who love to travel:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Policies that cover pre-existing service-related conditions</li>
          <li>Adventure travel coverage for active veterans</li>
          <li>Long-term travel insurance for extended stays abroad</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Income Protection Insurance</h2>
        <p>Safeguarding your income in case of illness or injury:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Policies designed to work alongside AFCS benefits</li>
          <li>Coverage for both service-related and non-service-related conditions</li>
          <li>Options for self-employed veterans</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/financial/pension-planning" class="text-decoration-none">Pension Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/investment-strategies" class="text-decoration-none">Investment Strategies</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/financial-advice" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Advice Services</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Insurance Consultation</h3>
            <p>Speak with an insurance specialist to find the right coverage for your needs.</p>
            <a href="/insurance-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book Consultation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
